{"tid":805102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★麥當勞「無飲管星期一」奶茶特飲除外　扮飲奶茶成功取飲管","createTime":"2018-09-03T13:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T23:23:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2adfaf50f0cf447585cb3722fe52b22459c5f2","tid":805102,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1823982/org/214e5eb11e13bbdec40c98bd4c563add.jpg/0rW2kniJZO-BNDNTHAQqsxdgWJutb8iFnTJiGp0yYho?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1823982%2Forg%2F214e5eb11e13bbdec40c98bd4c563add.jpg%2F0rW2kniJZO-BNDNTHAQqsxdgWJutb8iFnTJiGp0yYho%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=19588427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>冇飲管好唔方便　扮飲奶茶成功向店員拿飲管</strong><br />\n<br />\n同樣放學到麥當勞食午餐的吳同學指，點餐後店員向她表示不會派飲管後才知今日是「無飲管星期一」。點汽水沒有飲管，吳同學認為「冇飲管真係好唔方便」，所以當她返回座位後決定向店員索取飲管。吳同學續指店員曾問她喝甚麼飲料，她隨即回答奶茶後便獲得兩枝粗飲管。<br />\n<br />\n吳同學亦指知道麥當勞以後星期一不再派發飲管後，會自備飲管；但她同時會<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量避免星期一光顧麥當勞<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/230785/%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E-%E7%84%A1%E9%A3%B2%E7%AE%A1%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80-%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E7%89%B9%E9%A3%B2%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96-%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%89%AE%E9%A3%B2%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E5%8F%96%E9%A3%B2%E7%AE%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F230785%2F%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25B8%2580-%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E8%258C%25B6%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2596-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2589%25AE%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E8%258C%25B6%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E7%25AE%25A1&d=plTPkCoj89AXc0oqNvzSREbWhtBCnEJYRTWb